79  """
80  A callback function for IMU topics
81 
82  Arguments

84  data: sensor_msgs.msg.Imu

104  acceleration = utils.Vector3_to_np(data.linear_acceleration)
105 
106  dt = self.watch_dt.get_elapsed_time()
107  self.watch_dt.restart()
108  if self.is_sim and dt <= 0.9*self.sim_dt:
109  return

111  curr_angular_velocity = self.controller.joint_velocity(self.curr_joint_name)
112  angular_acceleration = (curr_angular_velocity - self.prev_angular_velocity) / dt
113  self.prev_angular_velocity = curr_angular_velocity
114 
115  joint_angles = self.controller.joint_angles
116 
117  # time

119  self.dynamic_acceleration_storage.append(

121  joint_name=self.curr_joint_name, # for each excited joint

123  data=np.r_[
124  acceleration,

126  t,

133  def goto_defined_pose(self, pose, rest_time, log=True):
134  positions, _, pose_name = pose[0], pose[1], pose[2] # noqa: F841
135  # first, move to the position from <robot>_positions.txt
136  # TODO: We have to ensure that commanded positions are reached

139 
140  self.curr_pose_name = pose_name
141  if log:
142  print(
143  'At Position: ' + pose_name,
144  map(int, np.rad2deg(np.array(positions)))

164  def collect_data(self, amplitudes, freqs, rest_time,
165  static_motion_record_time,
166  dynamic_motion_record_time):
167  """
168  This will move the joint of the robot arm like a sine wave
169  for all joints for all defined poses.
170  """
171  self.controller.set_joint_position_speed(speed=1.0)
172 
173  for pose in self.poses_list:
174  self.goto_defined_pose(pose, rest_time)
175  # Record for given time
176  self.record_static_motion(static_motion_record_time)
177 
178  for i, joint_name in enumerate(self.joint_names):
179  # Go to current setting position
180  if i != 0:
181  self.goto_defined_pose(pose, rest_time, log=False)
182 
183  # Prepare for recording dynamic motion
184  self.prepare_prev_states(joint_name)
185  self.start_watches(dynamic_motion_record_time)
186 
187  velocities = np.zeros(len(self.joint_names))
188  while True:
189  # time within motion
190  t = self.watch_dynamic_motion.get_elapsed_time()
191 
192  # Oscillated Velocity pattern
193  velocities[i] = amplitudes[i] * np.sin(2 * np.pi * freqs[i] * t)
194  self.controller.send_velocities(velocities)
195 
196  if self.watch_dynamic_motion.is_ended():
197  break
198 
199  if rospy.is_shutdown():
200  return
201  self.r.sleep()
202 
203  self.watch_dynamic_motion.stop()
204  rospy.sleep(0.1)

209 
210 
211  Arguments

213  `save`: `bool`
214  If the data will be saved
215

217  """
218  if clean_static:

220  else:

222 
223  if clean_dynamic:
224  dynamic_data = self.dynamic_acceleration_storage.clean_data(verbose)
225  else:
226  dynamic_data = self.dynamic_acceleration_storage.data
227 
228  if save:
229  rospy.loginfo('saving')
230  self.static_acceleration_storage.save(static_data)
231  self.dynamic_acceleration_storage.save(dynamic_data)
